						<p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-2">Send us your logo, text, or artwork in any vector format. Our team reviews for optimal machine compatibility.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="relative">
						<div class="absolute -left-[41px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
						<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">2. Digital Mockup</h4>
						<p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-2">We provide a realistic 3D preview of how your keychain will look with chosen materials and finishes.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="relative">
						<div class="absolute -left-[41px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
						<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">3. Precision Crafting</h4>
						<p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-2">State-of-the-art machinery carves, prints, and finishes your order with obsessive attention to detail.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="relative">
						<div class="absolute -left-[41px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
						<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">4. Hand Inspection</h4>
						<p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-2">Each piece undergoes a 5-point quality check before being packed in our premium eco-friendly sleeves.</p>
					</div>
